metadata.name: The Thinker
metadata.description:
This is my Genesis (First) 3D minted artwork.

This fascinating piece was inspired by the multi-layered 420 culture. The Thinker is contemplating lifes deepest questions, while spiritually inhaling herbs through an all natural Backwoods apparatus. Transcend time and space while going on your own vision quest.

*The owner can reach out to me for the 3D art file.
